title: 122: Operation Get Doug Laid
description: Doug, the MindPump producer, is also known as "the spinner" and "chimpy." He is typically behind the scenes making sure the show sounds good and that all that supports the show is kept up to date. Sal, Adam & Justin work him hard and have decided it is time to let Doug out of his box to have a little fun.
